    "text": "$$\n\\begin{aligned}\n& \\Leftrightarrow 6y - 3xy = \\frac{16}{\\sqrt{3}}x - xy \\Leftrightarrow 2xy - 6y + \\frac{16}{\\sqrt{3}}x = 0 \\\\\n& \\Leftrightarrow y(2x - 6) = -\\frac{16}{\\sqrt{3}}x \\Rightarrow y = \\frac{-16x}{\\sqrt{3}(2x - 6)} = \\frac{-8x}{\\sqrt{3}(x - 3)}\n\\end{aligned}\n$$"
